Package musicplayer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Main
    This project creates button listeners for switch 1-4 and perform led blinking on the Raspberry Pi using the Pi4J library and plays wav sound files.
    MusicManager
    This class is a simple java class for playing sound files of an playlist.
    Pi4jButtonListener  
    Sound
    This class implements a simple wav music player and using the MusicManger class for automatically playing next songs.
    WavFileReader
    A simple WavFileReader class.
